or the slippers placed carefully in a pocketed bag by family 
members who have left home for the day 
others just like the fun of it all 
yeah this stuff is interesting but the thing i really liked 
was all the old baseball cards that other family had 14yearold 
mark chace said recalling his visit to the gutermans home three 
months ago they were great 
