answer sims cautioned we are trying to look at every idea we can 
to reduce congestion including ideas that havent been thought of 
before 
among the other options authorities have studied are doubledeck 
freeways commuter and metro rails and invehicle television 
screens that show congestion and suggest alternate routes 
