vincennes were affected by the inability of radar operators to match 
the planes radar trace with digital direction altitude and speed 
information displayed on another screen 
ghafoor said the suit named the general electric co and other 
entities which designed and manufactured the radar equipment on 
board the uss vincennes 
a spokesman for ge based in fairfield conn said sunday the 
company had not seen the suit 
