a june 21 temblor measuring 37 occurred in the same area june 
21 pechmann said 
mondays quake was felt in box elder and salt lake counties 
pechmann said 
the richter scale is a measure of ground motion as recorded on 
seismographs every increase of one number means a tenfold increase 
in magnitude thus a reading of 75 reflects an earthquake 10 times 
stronger than one of 65 
an earthquake of 35 on the richter scale can cause slight damage 
in the local area 4 moderate damage and 5 considerable damage 
</TEXT>
</DOC>

